title: [FSX/P3D] Ants Airplanes Eaglet LSA v1.21
description:
This is the latest version of Ant's Airplanes Eaglet LSA for you guys.

This has been patched to the latest version for you and does NOT require any further patching at the moment.

Remove the old shortcuts from your Start menu BEFORE installing this to prevent duplicate shortcuts. As far as I know this can be installed on top of the old version, but a clean install is RECOMMENDED as always.

Please SEED this package if you like it; I can't seed everything forever!

Enjoy!
